    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1868-06-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1868-06-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="360"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d360">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Señor Romero</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Mexico in the United States</hi>, <hi
                                rend="italic">Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-06-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 27, 1868.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary</hi>: In calling your attention to a note
                    which I addressed to Mr. Hunter on the 16th instant, I have the honor to
                    transmit to you the copy of a communication from the consul of Mexico in New
                    York, dated the 15th instant, in which he sends me the copy of a dispatch from
                    the consul of Mexico in New Orleans, with an annex, dated the 16th, relating to
                    the projected expedition organizing in that city for the purpose of invading
                    Matamoras, by common report.</p>
                <p>I take the occasion to repeat the assurances of my distinguished
                    consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>M. ROMERO.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
